---
import Button from '../../Button.astro'
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-center">
      A bit about me.
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 items-start">
      <!-- Photo placeholder -->
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 mx-auto md:mx-0">
        <div class="w-40 h-40 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-storehouse-200 to-emerald-200 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
          <!-- Placeholder for photo - shows initials as fallback -->
          <span class="font-display text-4xl text-storehouse-700">JR</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-center text-sm text-slate-500">JR</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio content -->
      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          I've spent 20+ years in real estate — as an agent, sales manager, and broker. I've seen what happens when people buy too much house.
        </p>

        <p>
          But I've also seen the freedom that comes from leaving margin.
        </p>

        <p>
          I'm a husband, a dad, and a Christian. I believe what the Bible teaches about money -- that it should serve life, not the other way around.
        </p>

        <div class="pt-4">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">
            Other projects:
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-base">
            <li>
              <span class="text-slate-700">The Candid Agent</span>
              <span class="text-slate-400"> — Honest real estate guidance</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="text-slate-700">Good News Garden</span>
              <span class="text-slate-400"> — Faith, family, and flourishing</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Sign off -->
    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 italic">
        Thanks for being here.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-lg text-slate-600">
        — JR
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <Button href="/waitlist" variant="primary" size="lg">
        Join the Waitlist
      </Button>
      <Button href="/philosophy" variant="secondary" size="lg">
        Read My Philosophy
      </Button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
